{{see|Grab}}

==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-æb|-æb]]

===Verb===
'''to grab''' ([[grabs]], [[grabbed]], [[grabbing]])
# to make a [[sudden]] [[grasp]]ing or [[clutch]]ing motion (at something)
# to [[restrain]] someone; to [[arrest]]
# to [[grip]] the [[attention]]; to [[enthrall]]
===Noun===
'''grab'''
# the act of grabbing something or someone
# a [[mechanical]] [[device]] that grabs
